Repository license notice
=========================

This repository is distributed under multiple licenses depending on the
material type. Unless a more specific notice is provided in a file or folder,
the following scopes apply:

1. CAD / hardware design files

   License: CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal
   SPDX identifier: CERN-OHL-S-2.0
   Full text: https://spdx.org/licenses/CERN-OHL-S-2.0.html

   This applies to hardware source and design outputs, including files such as
   .step, .stl, .3mf, and other mechanical/CAD artifacts.

2. Images / documentation

   License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
   SPDX identifier: CC-BY-4.0
   Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

   This applies to documentation, drawings, screenshots, diagrams, photos,
   explanatory text, and similar documentation assets.

3. Arduino / control code

   License: MIT License
   SPDX identifier: MIT
   Full text: https://spdx.org/licenses/MIT.html

   This applies to Arduino sketches, firmware, scripts, and other control code
   unless a file or folder provides a different license notice.

Attribution and notices
-----------------------

When reusing repository materials, preserve existing copyright, license, and
attribution notices where present. For CERN-OHL-S-2.0 hardware design files,
follow the source, modification, distribution, and notice requirements in that
license.
